{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2013/06/use-magic-lantern/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/learn/","name":"摄影学习与折腾"},{"path":"/category/film/","name":"独立电影与短片"}],"tags":[{"name":"Magic Lantern","path":"/tag/magic-lantern/"},{"name":"佳能","path":"/tag/canon-camera/"},{"name":"固件","path":"/tag/firmware/"},{"name":"城市","path":"/tag/city/"},{"name":"夜景","path":"/tag/night-scene/"},{"name":"摄影","path":"/tag/photography/"}],"featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/a456be20c5356b99ab547a88bb3deb1c/e737e/MG_6465-Panorama_.jpg","srcSet":"/static/a456be20c5356b99ab547a88bb3deb1c/e737e/MG_6465-Panorama_.jpg 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/a456be20c5356b99ab547a88bb3deb1c/e7773/MG_6465-Panorama_.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}},"path":"/2013/06/use-magic-lantern/","date":"2013-06-09T09:39:02.000Z","excerpt":"为宜昌华祥商业中心拍摄一组关于它们项目的夜景风光照片。 户外的夜景拍摄要关注的时机很重要，当中包括了天气、日落 … ","title":"巧用Magic Lantern拍摄城市夜景风光-一个拍摄案例","content":"<p>为宜昌华祥商业中心拍摄一组关于它们项目的夜景风光照片。</p>\n<p>户外的夜景拍摄要关注的时机很重要，当中包括了天气、日落时间、日落方向，需要提前做好功课。这次夜景拍摄结合了长时间曝光和全景接片。为了达到稳定触发快门的目的，在没有快门线的情况下，我们使用了Canon的破解固件Magic Lantern中的声音遥控快门功能，当然牢固的三脚架必不可少。</p>\n<p><iframe height=405 width=720 src=\"https://player.youku.com/embed/XNTY1MjgzNzg4\" frameborder=0 allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7rihYsC-K8I\" target=\"_blank\">在YouTube上观看</a></p>\n<p>有的朋友看了后对这个MagicLantern（<a href=\"http://www.magiclantern.fm/\" target=\"_blank\">项目官网www.magiclantern.fm</a>）固件感兴趣了，这个项目充分挖掘了佳能的数字单反性能。以后来出一个安装和使用MagicLantern的介绍，请关注。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/MG_6465-Panorama_.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1298\" alt=\"华祥商业中心夜景\" src=\"https://archived-blog.berl